{"annotations": {}, "citation": {"authors": ["Colson P", "Devaux CA", "Raoult D", "Rolain JM"], "date": "2020-03-12", "db": "PubMed", "db_id": "32171740", "db_name": "International journal of antimicrobial agents", "first": "Devaux CA", "last": "Raoult D", "pages": "105938"}, "evidence": "Chloroquine was shown to inhibit quinone reductase 2 [56], a structural neighbour of UDP-N-acetylglucosamine 2-epimerases [57] that are involved in the biosynthesis of sialic acids.
